product.name: 110V LED Under Cabinet Lighting,17inch LED Strip Light Bar with 6ft Power Cord,Magnetic Installation,Super Slim Counter Light,Reading Desk Lamp for Kitchen/Work Table.(White 6000K)
product.description: Package Includes: 1 x LED Light Bar (The lamp body adopts integrated sealed plastic shell,insulated from the outside to ensure safety.) 2 x Small magnets 2 x Small Steel disks 4 x Double-sided adhesive pads
product.bullet_points:
• LED light source, No stroboscopic, low energy consumption, long life,safety eye protection. White(6000K) version makes it very bright.Natural white(4000K) version is more soft and natural.
• The under cabinet lights with simple plug and play design, can be used on any standard US wall power socket or power strip.No power adapter required that save space on sockets; button switch ON/OFF control, easy to operation,there is no complicated motion sensor, it is not easy to break, more power-saving and durable.
• Easy magnetic installation,no need tools, just take one minute, use magnets and double-sided adhesive pads, you can install the LED light bar anywhere and remove it when needed without damaging the furniture.
• Refer to the structure of most cabinets, we set the length of the lamp cord to 6 ft and the switch in the middle, which is convenient to connect to your wall socket and use handy. In addition, considering that there may be a humid and oily environment in the kitchen, we chose a transparent silver vinyl sheathed lamp cord, which has the advantages of resists moisture, abrasion and anti-oxidation.
• This is a simple brilliant led under-counter lighting with clean lines and straight forward function.Suitable for Kitchen Cabinet/Desk/shelves/Bookshelf/Closet/sink/ Showcase/workbench etc.
